Class BoxSignRequest.Info.BoxSignRequestSignFiles

    BoxSignRequest.Info

    public class BoxSignRequest.Info.BoxSignRequestSignFiles
extends Object
    List of files that will be signed, which are copies of the original source files. A new version of these files are created as signers sign and can be downloaded at any point in the signing process.

      • getIsReadyToDownload

        public boolean getIsReadyToDownload()
        Gets the flag indicating whether a change to the document is processing and the PDF may be out of date. It is recommended to wait until processing has finished before downloading the PDF. Webhooks are not sent until processing has been completed.
        Returns:
        true if files are ready to download, otherwise false.
